						               													<description>Pr&amp;oacute;ba Ognia (The Trial of fire) is a cooperative game with One versus Many mode. Players work together as a group of firefighters trying to overcome the Disaster.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Base game contains 3 different scenarios - one full cooperative (against Electricity) and two in One versus Many mode (against Fire and Flood).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During each of their turns, firefighters play two cards that allows them to perform actions: Move, Help, Scout or Fight. Firefighters move around the city, find dangers and victims and try to fullfill scenario goals, whereas Disaster plays card to give them stress, destroy buildings or kill victims.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Base game contains 90 cards for firefighters in 6 prepared decks, but also allows players to mix them up and create their own custom decks. More cards are going to be available in upcoming expansions and distribute during series of local events.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game is based on real firefighters actions and was made in close cooperation with Orlen Foundation, that helps local volunteer fire deps.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
